&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>-&amp;gt; x*3하면: [333, 303030, 343434, 555, 999] 정렬: [34, 3, 30, 5, 9]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="코드">
 코드
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%bd%94%eb%93%9c">#&lt;/a>
